<plot>In the same genre of shows as "Real People" (1979) and "That's Incredible" (1980), this show focused on the interesting and unusual in the animal world. Features ranged from documentary-style descriptions of little-known wild animals to stories about everyday pets that had been trained to perform extraordinary feats.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?605309</url></doc>
